      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      270.32,
      526.33,
      283.36
    ],
    "text": "I am mindful that the learned Counsel for the appellant has contended that the following",
