      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      310.04,
      305.4,
      323.08
    ],
    "text": "favour of the appellant as mitigating factors.",
