      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      678.73,
      526.36,
      691.77
    ],
    "text": "convictions or pending cases. Also, seventeen years have passed since the incident, and",
